WEBVTT

00:00:00.333 --> 00:00:02.669
If the Department does not promote an Employee due to a

00:00:02.736 --> 00:00:05.772
lack of work or funds, the Department will conduct

00:00:05.839 --> 00:00:09.409
subsequent reviews at six-month intervals and promote the

00:00:09.476 --> 00:00:13.446
Employee or provide the Employee-and the Local-a written

00:00:13.513 --> 00:00:17.550
notification and explanation within seven calendar days.


